Title: Stuart Turner Monsoon Universal 2 Bar Twin Shwr Pump
Description: Designed for vented systems, the 2 bar Stuart Turner Monsoon fully automatic universal twin pump boosts both hot and cold water supplies in balance and is suitable for both positive and negative head applications. The Monsoon Universal doesn't require a gravity flow of water to start, so it's ideal for pressurising a supply where outlets are higher than the water source, such as in a loft conversion or where it's not clear if a positive flow of water exists.
